LINQ use scenarios <ol> <li> <p><code>LINQ</code> to Entities - Process data from a database: C#<pre><code>var customers = dbContext.Customers
    .Where(c =&gt; c.City == "London")
    .OrderBy(c =&gt; c.Name);
</code></pre> This query returns all customers from London, sorted by name.</p> </li> <li> <p><code>LINQ</code> to XML - Parsing and querying XML documents: C#<pre><code>XDocument doc = XDocument.Load("file.xml");
