    .Where(e =&gt; (int)e.Element("price") &gt; 20)
    .Select(e =&gt; e.Element("title").Value);
</code></pre> This query selects the titles of all books in an XML document with a price over 20.</p> </li> <li> <p><code>LINQ</code> to JSON - Querying data from a web service: C#<pre><code>var client = new WebClient();
