</code></pre> This code queries a JSON web service for items of a certain type</p> </li> <li> <p><code>LINQ</code> to objects - process data in memory: C#<pre><code>var productsByCategory = products
    .GroupBy(p =&gt; p.Category)
    .Select(g =&gt; new { Category = g.Key, Count = g.Count() });
</code></pre> This query groups a list of products by category and counts the number of   products in each category.</p> </li> <li> <p><code>LINQ</code> to ADO.NET - Querying data from a datasets; C#<pre><code>var products = dataSet.Tables["Products"]
